snippet.title: Ourlands - Official Developer Video | Black Voices in Gaming 2024
snippet.description: Learn more about developer Graham Reed's journey in the game industry, and watch as Reed introduces Ourlands in this video for the upcoming cozy island builder where you craft bespoke little lands for quirky little characters. Ourlands will be available on PC.
